Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:30.39,Title4,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm and\NStress
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.99,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want normalcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.99,0:24:20.31,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try living differently from most people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:25.90,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought it would affect so many others...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.29,0:24:27.21,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:29.32,Default-no margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Storm and Stress.
